{"tid":1965924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"約翰遜轉出深切治療部","createTime":"2020-04-09T19:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T20:42:27.000Z","uid":348984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"13c9d0eca988b28ecb0cc21f598180018a6d8e73","tid":1965924,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T19:57:03.000Z","msg":"感染武漢肺炎的英國首相約翰遜離開深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相府發表聲明稱，約翰遜今晚被轉出深切治療部，將繼續留在普通病房。發言人指，約翰遜目前精神狀態狀態「極好」。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜是在星期日因為病徵持續而入院，星期一因為病情惡化而轉入深切治療部。"},{"pid":"f6c82295452de8576f4b00d557ef03a7a9d3325f","tid":1965924,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T19:57:30.000Z","msg":"一日唔死一日唔會醒"},{"pid":"b99ddf88b89b2945648530959807d94c75f4cdbb","tid":1965924,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T19:58:29.000Z","msg":"咁佢仲用唔用華為？"},{"pid":"9a9140a39c05285dc501c2ce0aa5a804891ac784","tid":1965924,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:39:51.000Z","msg":"仲奶唔奶共呀？？？？"},{"pid":"521b2d44289dc02fde5b0d73c1852c55c6a27ccc","tid":1965924,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:40:09.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"66fa5934d30ac68467209307a1021bac690b0679","tid":1965924,"uid":343033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:41:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2e2bbd10340989fecfd57f01b0634e90dd2ee2d","tid":1965924,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T20:42:27.000Z","msg":"用緊華為大陸應該俾英國班人仲早知道佢病況"}]}